_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Brad Beckett</h5>\r\n<h6>Vice President of Sales and Marketing</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Darryl Levesque</h5>\r\n<h6>Director of Technology Solutions</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Michael De Cesare</h5>\r\n<h6>Vice President, Finance and Human Resources</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/4"][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[person src="" name="" post="" twitter="" facebook="" skype="" linkedin="" mail="" link=""]\r\n<h5>Mirella Lebeau</h5>\r\n<h6>VP of Client Support and Managed Services</h6>\r\n[/person]\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]Testimonials[blockquote]Through Kanatek’s Managed Service offerings, we have reduced the complexity of our backup/restore processes while increasing reliability. Their approach has provided solutions that are sensitive to our unique requirements, allowing us to focus our IT resources on more strategic initiatives.[/blockquote][blockquote align="pull-right"]I have been involved as a Project Manager for Torstar Corporation involving a Backup and Recovery Project. The key integrating company involved was KTI Kanatek Technologies Inc. They have proven to be an extremely strong partner with deep capabilities in data protection. From the beginning, Kanatek understood the criticality of our infrastructure stabilization project and has consistently performed on the phases of our Symantec Enterprise Backup, Archiving, Deduplication and Quantum products. With a strong project manager and a flexible delivery team, I would recommend Kanatek as a company that has an excellent professional services staff.[/blockquote][blockquote]Kanatek''s backup and recovery managed services team provides Nortel with the needed resources and tools to ensure the availability of our data through cost-effective solutions and unparalleled support. Data is everything and Kanatek helps us ensure the availability of our valuable resources. You can rebuild the network or rebuild a server, but you cannot rebuild your data if you lose it.[/blockquote][blockquote align="pull-right"]I would like to compliment Kanatek for their service support. CIBC Mellon holds extremely high standards for vendors and Kanatek has consistently exceeded expectations in their proactive preparation, knowledge and response time. The Kanatek team has been attentive, patient, and committed to forging a strong partnership with our organization. I am confident that we can build on this relationship and look forward to continuing to work with Kanatek.[/blockquote][/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/1"][vc_column_text]Partners[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '4-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-24 20:54:15', '2015-01-24 20:54:15', '', 4, 'http://localhost/kanatek/2015/01/24/4-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
